Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建议
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在水中使用光束兵器效率低下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应权衡对友军的损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:00:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此…
